It is a test task given by a potential employer.

Task required Android application that lets inserting images into a html file. Images can be taken from camera or from a file on sd card.
File selection should be filterable by file name and scan for image files should be in background so UI does not block.
Filtered results should be also updated dynamically when new pictures are found.

